<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Erişim Kapatıldı | NOXY</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* grid arka plan efekti */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 60px 60px;
            animation: gridMove 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes gridMove {
            0% {
                transform: translate(0, 0);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translate(60px, 60px);
            }
        }

        /* parlayan orb */
        .orb {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(120px);
            opacity: 0.15;
            animation: float 12s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .orb-1 {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: #6c5ce7;
            top: -150px;
            left: -100px;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .orb-2 {
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: #a855f7;
            bottom: -150px;
            right: -100px;
            animation-delay: -4s;
        }

        .orb-3 {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: #3b82f6;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            animation-delay: -8s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1);
            }
            25% {
                transform: translate(30px, -30px) scale(1.1);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translate(-20px, 20px) scale(0.95);
            }
            75% {
                transform: translate(-30px, -20px) scale(1.05);
            }
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 50px;
            background: rgba(15, 15, 20, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(40px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 32px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 32px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6),
                inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            max-width: 520px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .lock-icon-wrapper {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .lock-icon-wrapper::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -4px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent 60%);
            -webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
            -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
            mask-composite: exclude;
        }

        .lock-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5));
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a855f7, #6c5ce7);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 48px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a855f7, #6c5ce7, transparent);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 24px auto;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .discord-card {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 14px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 16px 28px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1.2);
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .discord-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.15), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
        }

        .discord-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 
                0 20px 40px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.2),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.2);
        }

        .discord-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .discord-card:hover .discord-icon {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 16px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.8));
        }

        .discord-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1.2);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .discord-username {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #e0e0ff;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .discord-card:hover .discord-username {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .footer-text {
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 40px 28px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .discord-card {
                padding: 14px 22px;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    <div class="orb orb-3"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="lock-icon-wrapper">
            <!-- Kilit SVG ikonu -->
            <svg class="lock-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>
            <span class="highlight">NOXY</span> TARAFINDAN<br>ERİŞİME KAPATILMIŞTIR
        </h1>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <p class="message">
            Bu site yönetici tarafından erişime kapatılmıştır.<br>
            Detaylı bilgi için aşağıdaki Discord hesabı üzerinden<br>iletişime geçebilirsiniz.
        </p>

        <!-- Discord bağlantısı -->
        <a href="https://discord.com/users/noxyorj" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="discord-card">
            <!-- Discord logosu SVG -->
            <svg class="discord-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
